Package: xbrlr
Type: Package
Title: Tools for XBRL Taxonomy Analytics and Visualization in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person(given = "Brad", family = "West", email = "brad.g.west@gmail.com",
               role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools for visualizing and analyzing XBRL
    taxonomy data.  Primary functionality is devoted to visualising XBRL 
    taxonomy network tree graphs.  This package is not intended for external
    use, but rather is used as a structure for formating a larger scale
    and ongoing data analysis.
